## Icons & Buttons
- Icons: Semi-transparent gradients; glow on hover.
- Buttons:
  - Background: Glass opacity 60-80%.
  - Hover: Scale 1.05x; shadow enhance.
  - Active: Border flash; 0.2s bounce ease-out.
- Touch targets: ≥44px mobile.

## UX Principles
1. Content-Centric: Glass backgrounds; no text obscurity.
2. Hierarchy: Transparency/shadows/contrast for levels.
3. Consistency: Uniform opacity/radius/shadow.
4. Adaptability: Responsive media queries for blur.
5. Performance: Fallback flattened design.

Test: Varied backgrounds; readability validation.

